The paper deals with using deep learning algorithms for image classification and text recognition, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques for information retrieval (cs.IR) and classification (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in general.
